*Of course there is the work of the Church, and the seflessness of friendship, &quot;but what of the Mark?&quot; he muses*<br>
&quot;I guess I rely on the Tears vision as a whole to guide me from day to day, there is no conflict with the guiding will of Tunare.&quot;<br>
*Callmed asks me about the Mark*<br>
&quot;of all the peoples of Norrath, it is those of the Fairer Sex that seem most interested in scarifacation, in general&quot; I say with a mock scholarly air.<br>
&quot;But as to its True nature, it is an Enigma&quot;<br>
*Callmed cuffs me up side the head*<br>
&quot;he must have hear my words differenly i guess&quot; I thought...<br>
<br>
